About us
Many people would dreamt and believed that, they will do something amazing in this era but don’t have good or exact platform for help or support?
No worry. Robotics Club, BMU is here! To induct you into the rapidly expanding world of robotics. One on one interaction and guidance, workshops, events and along with fun and enjoyment as must. Mainly this club is a student body which finds its place under interests and anxiety. 
With this motto of promoting technology, creativity and innovation, the club has built up. We even understood that, this fast and evolving era is the perfect time line to setup or shape our future.
   We’re changing the way people think on the clubs.
